meta {
  name: School construction - enrollment aggregate
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/datasets/education_registry/student/aggregates/by_school_grade_status
  body: none
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{aggregateKey}}
}

docs {
  Step 3 of 3: School construction follow-up workflow.
  Runs enrollment aggregate to see current student counts at school sch-3001.
  Uses planning_analyst persona (aggregateKey).
  Together with steps 5-6 this gives: construction timeline (public works), current
  operational state (education school record), and enrollment load (this aggregate).
  Expected: 200 with student counts per grade+status for the school.
}
